recordTypes.name: New Construction - Single Family Attached
recordTypes.description: Please apply here for Twin Homes, Townhomes, etc.

recordTypes.name: Building Permit - Residential
recordTypes.description: Please apply here for Residential Building Permits.  Deck, Screen Porch, Remodel, Addition, Basement Finish, Accessory Structures, Swimming Pool, New Window/Door (altered opening), Draintile.

recordTypes.name: Residential Re-Roof, Re-Side, or Windows/Doors
recordTypes.description:
Please apply here for Residential Re-Roofing, Re-Siding, Replacement of Window(s) and/or Door(s) (within existing openings).


NOTE: If any window/door openings need to be altered, please apply for "Building Permit - Residential".

recordTypes.name: Building Permit - Commercial
recordTypes.description: Please apply here for Commercial Building Permits. Tenant Finish, Remodel, Addition, Roofing, Accessory Structure, Window/Doors.

recordTypes.name: Plumbing - Residential
recordTypes.description: Please apply here for Residential Water Softener, Water Heater, Drinking Water System, Plumbing Fixture(s).

recordTypes.name: Mechanical - Residential
recordTypes.description: Please apply here for Residential (New or Replacement) Air Conditioner, Furnace, Boiler, Fireplace, Gasline, Garage Heater.

recordTypes.name: Fire Suppression or Alarm System Permit
Solar Permit
recordTypes.description: Please apply here for Solar Panels.

recordTypes.name: Septic System Permit
recordTypes.description: Please apply here for Type I, II, III, IV, V  Septic System (New or Replace), Drainfield Repair, Tank(s) (New or Replace).

recordTypes.name: Sign Permit
recordTypes.description: Please apply here for Sign Permits. Freestanding (Monument or Pylon), New Wall Sign, Sign Face Replacement.

recordTypes.name: Master Plan Review
recordTypes.description: Contact Deb at 763-473-8847 for instructions on submitting for Master Plan Review.

recordTypes.name: Wetland Permit
recordTypes.description:
Please apply here for Wetland Permits.  
Wetland Delineation, No Loss / Exemption Request, Wetland Estimate.
